column5: Im heading out for some fishing on a local lake was down there yesterday about 4-6 inches of ice. Lotsa fellas out on sleds, landed a nice large mouth yesterday first time for everything i guess bringing the camera today hopefully have some pics for you all later on in the day.  im out
Hey Licker,  Are you meeting up with chewmytoe?  What kinda pics will you have?
No but im pretty sure eatmytoenail is on way...
No pics me and smellmyfinger got skunked......couple good knockoffs on the tip ups got the hut out better luck this weekend hopefully
Thanks for the report  Sorry you and smelly got skunked.  Carressmycanker sends his love.
largemouth through the ice wow never seenm that before...hears about smallies but thats it

I've caught both smallmouth and largemouth through the ice.  Last year I got a 16 inch largemouth on the first weekend in March, got it on a live minnow while fishing for pike.  The next day, while fishing for perch on Simcoe, in 39 fow, I hooked what I thought was a whitefish, but ended up being a 19.5 inch smallmouth.  Got her on a 1/32 oz teardrop and maggots.
Hey Lickmyarmpit, did Scratchmyballs go with you, I hear he was itchin to go!  Joey
LOL .... the only question I have ... is what the heck was ticklemytouche doing during all of this ?
I can see lickmyarmpit is going to have a tough time for a while to get a straight respectable answer Nipissing....AKA "pullmyfinger"
Just stay away from SmellMyButt, his fishing tips stink and he always gets skunked!  LOL
